{"tid":2054883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★私營龕位十多萬起跳 殯儀師：「有錢才有資格死」","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:49:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"850ead0b334c0686639364b4506b253d1e4e4fcd","tid":2054883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"私營骨灰龕位停止出售前，位處方便位置的骨灰龕場的龕位價格，已在十多萬起跳。至於沙田萬佛寺等比較難到的地方，則會相應便宜一點。他亦預期私人龕位或會在政府發牌後，會因應補地價等費用再加價。<br />\n<br />\n殯儀師陳達仁估計，公營骨灰龕場的政策不明朗，會導致私營骨灰龕位的價格更加高，變相正在延續「有錢才有資格死」這回事。<br />\n<br />\n「很明顯，政府現時的做法，鼓勵了私營骨灰龕的（炒賣）風氣，」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_582247_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_582247_0&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=9a4194bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_582247_0&h=f838a4b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_582247_0</a>"},{"pid":"45822d5d2292bffe516058b142a24bca29a2fdfb","tid":2054883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751ade92a8a20d73afe06072fd508fda67bf28f3","tid":2054883,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"我寧願灑落大海算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e111f9b974bf5b0373c932dad29a31febd88aa","tid":2054883,"uid":247184,"l